body:

[Steps to install Java JDK + Java FX Scenebuilder + InteliJ IDE](https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/2016.1/preparing-for-javafx-application-development.html) on Arch Linux (with yaourt to access AUR):

<pre>
$ yaourt -S jdk
$ yaourt -S javafx-scenebuilder-bin
# pacman -S intellij-idea-community-edition
</pre>
